Package com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client

Defines the Rhizosphere visualization widget and all the main interfaces required to configure and instantiate a Rhizosphere visualization within GWT.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CustomRhizosphereMetaModel Allows POJOs used as Rhizosphere models to configure the metadata and characteristics of custom attributes not handled by the annotation-based mechanism provided by RhizosphereModelAttribute.
CustomRhizosphereModel Allows POJOs used as Rhizosphere models to expose custom attributes not handled by the annotation-based mechanism provided by RhizosphereModelAttribute.
RhizosphereCallback Callback interface to collect the outcome of programmatic requests sent to a Rhizosphere visualization.
RhizosphereCallback1<T> Callback interface equivalent to RhizosphereCallback that accepts an extra typed parameter as notification payload.
RhizosphereLazyPanel.RhizosphereBuilder<T> Builder interface the RhizosphereLazyPanel delegates the actual Rhizosphere visualization building to.
RhizosphereMapping<T> Maps functionalities between externally defined POJOs and the object model Rhizosphere requires to operate.
RhizosphereModel Marker interface that identifies POJOs to use as Rhizopshere visualization models.
RhizosphereRenderer<T> A renderer provides a visual representation of visualization models.
 

Class Summary
Rhizosphere<T> Widget wrapping a Rhizosphere visualization.
RhizosphereLazyPanel<T> Helper panel to simplify the addition of a Rhizosphere visualization in a GWT application, hiding all the steps necessary to inject the Rhizosphere APIs in the GWT application.
RhizosphereLoader Loader to inject Rhizosphere javascript libraries into a GWT host page.
RhizosphereMetaModel Enumerates and characterizes the attributes of Rhizosphere visualization models.
RhizosphereMetaModel.Attribute A single metamodel attribute.
RhizosphereModelPosition Simple wrapper to declare an explicit positioning of a Rhizosphere model within the visualization viewport.
RhizosphereModelRef An opaque pointer holding a reference to a Rhizosphere model.
RhizosphereOptions<T> Rhizosphere configuration options.
RhizosphereOptions.LayoutConstraints A map of constraints for the area that Rhizosphere will use to lay out models' renderings.
RhizosphereSelectionManager The Selection Manager keeps track of which models within a Rhizosphere visualization are currently selected, deselected, hidden or focused upon.
RhizosphereUserAgent<T> The UserAgent is an high-level interface to programmatically drive a Rhizosphere visualization like a user would do.
 

Enum Summary
RhizosphereKind Enumeration of the datatypes ('kinds' in Rhizosphere terminology) that can be assigned to Rhizosphere model attributes.
RhizosphereMetaModel.DateClusterCriteria Enumeration of valid clustering criteria for Attribute#setDateClusterBy(DateClusterCriteria) settings.
RhizosphereOptions.LogLevel Enumeration of logging levels that the Rhizosphere visualization can use for client-side logging.
RhizosphereOptions.PanningMode Enumeration of the panning modes that the Rhizosphere visualization allows for scrolling and panning gestures.
RhizosphereOptions.ResizeTrackingMode Enumeration of the resize tracking modes that the Rhizosphere visualization supports.
RhizosphereOptions.SelectionMode Enumeration of selection modes that the Rhizosphere visualization allows.
 

Exception Summary
RhizosphereException Exception thrown whenever something goes wrong in any Rhizosphere part.
 

Annotation Types Summary
RhizosphereModelAttribute Method annotation to expose POJO getters as attributes of Rhizosphere models.
 

Package com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client Description

Defines the Rhizosphere visualization widget and all the main interfaces required to configure and instantiate a Rhizosphere visualization within GWT.
